                    <span>The book is pretty much suitable for students who has finished  high school maths but requires revision on maths for computing. A few chapters are simple enough for students to run over quickly. There is a  supplementary questions and solved questions with working for student to  understand and practice on. Overall the book is good enough to refresh your  memory on computer maths.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">very poorly structured</div>
